descriptor.name: Loaded with internationally acclaimed Epsom Salt, our Epsom Energy Body Wash not only cleans but also leaves you fresh, calm, and ready to take on the day! This Body Wash works fast to replenish your body's lost energy, from de-cramping tense muscles to relaxing sore spots. Sprinkled with lavender and chamomile aromatherapy, this is the ultimate bath solution to begin and end your day on an uplifting note!

Rise & shine! Improve mood & energise mind in one quick pump. The Happy Hormones Stress Relief Mist is an aromatherapy blend packed with feel-good ingredients. Use for yoga, meditation, at work, and during stressful moments. Infused with energizing eucalyptus and spearmint, you'll be ready to tackle anything - hectic meetings, exam worries, crazy traffic, and more! Get ready to "Om" your stress away!

Maximum relief, minimal effort! Our Headache Roll On is a lightweight, no-fuss formula for headache & migraine relief, powered with metal roller ball tech for smooth application. Say goodbye to popping pills - peppermint heals naturally and lavender extracts induce calm. The new bag essential to keep blue light strain away! Your best buddy for high screen time and sleepless nights.

Rescuing your hard-working hands that never get a break! Powered with cinnamon extracts & cooling menthol, our lightweight Hand Pain Cream melts hand cramps, pain in finger joints, wrists & thumb, while shea butter & ceramides make skin feather-soft. A pain-relieving and moisturising super-combo - laptop users, gamers, smartphone addicts can thank their lucky stars. Apply it and carry on with your day!

No more tossing & turning! Let us usher you into a cocoon of restful sleep with Transdermal Magnesium Therapy. Our Magnesium Sleep Support Body Lotion absorbs into skin for superb relaxation & muscle recovery, so you can power off your device, say adios to late working hours, and hello to deep, uninterrupted sleep – all without having to count sheep! Feel light & airy with magnesium, lavender & chamomile!

A lightening bolt of energy for your early mornings with our Transdermal Magnesium Therapy! This is no ordinary lotion. Sure, it nourishes and hydrates. But our Magnesium Stress Relief Body Lotion will quickly become your go-to stress relief for gearing up for long days, strenuous workouts, and when you need a pick me up. Perfect for pre-work mindfulness, post-workout recovery, and those pesky body aches.

Say goodbye to sticky ointments! India's first cryotherapy Pain Relief Roll On delivers quick relief from pain in shoulder, neck, lower back after long sitting hours and muscle recovery after sports. Don't shy away from using in sensitive areas - thigh, hamstring, groin, abs. This Pain Relief Roll On heals by cooling and is great smelling. It's perfect for on the go, apply anytime pain strikes.

Not your average pain spray! India's first cryotherapy pain relief spray for an instant & great smelling solution to all pains. Our formula delivers a smooth recovery from back pain after long sitting days, knee pain after running, muscle soreness after gym, and more! Use at home, at work, or after gym. Our pain relief spray is like an ice pack in a bottle! Bonus: we don't smell bad.

Say goodnight to insomnia & fatigue with Starry Nights Sleep Mist! A blend of Lavender-Chamomile aromatherapy, this night time remedy is the perfect natural sleep support to help you snooze faster, deeper, and with no disruption. No matter how many late hours you've worked or how much you've been on your phone - wake up feeling refreshed always! An unmissable step in your bedtime routine.
